title: Bingo Hell
description: Bingo Hell is a 2021 American horror thriller film directed by Gigi Saul Guerrero from a screenplay that she co-wrote with Shane McKenzie and Perry Blackshear. The film is the fifth installment in the anthological Welcome to the Blumhouse film series. The film stars L. Scott Caldwell, Adriana Barraza and Joshua Caleb Johnson.
